reviewText: My whole Scandinavian club enjoyed the video.

There appears to be a dearth of material in DVD American format about this unbelievable historic ship ! This video treated the recovery of the hulk from the Stockholm harbor . It is written in a terse, scholarly format.. I would have liked more color illustrations of it present condition within it's permanent museum home !close -ups of the Dutch, German carvings  could have embellished its pages. But, still, a valuable contribution!
